## 📋 Best Practice Checklist

```markdown
- [x] No `with`
- [x] Explicit destructuring
- [x] nixfmt-rfc-style formatting
- [x] Namespaced options
- [x] Prefer let-in over rec
- [x] Platform guards for {Linux,Darwin}
- [x] lib.mkIf/mkMerge for conditions
- [x] Assert for validation
- [x] Use config.home.homeDirectory
```

---

## 🏗️ Patterns

### Conditional Config

```nix
config = lib.mkMerge [
  (lib.mkIf cfg.enable { services.x.enable = true; })
  (lib.mkIf (cfg.enable && cfg.monitoring.enable) { services.prometheus.exporters.x.enable = true; })
  { services.x.port = lib.mkDefault 8080; }
];
```

### Cross-Platform Systems

```nix
systems = [ "x86_64-linux" "aarch64-linux" "aarch64-darwin" "x86_64-darwin" ];
```

### Platform-native deps

```nix
nativeBuildInputs = [
  pkgs.python313 pkgs.uv
] ++ lib.optionals pkgs.stdenv.isLinux [ pkgs.stdenv.cc.cc.lib pkgs.zlib ]
  ++ lib.optionals pkgs.stdenv.isDarwin [
    pkgs.darwin.apple_sdk.frameworks.Security
    pkgs.darwin.apple_sdk.frameworks.SystemConfiguration
  ];
```

### Platform-conditional config

```nix
let isDarwin = pkgs.stdenv.hostPlatform.isDarwin;
    homeDir = config.home.homeDirectory;
in
config = lib.mkMerge [
  { programs.git.enable = true; }
  (lib.mkIf pkgs.stdenv.isLinux { home.packages = [ pkgs.zathura ]; })
  (lib.mkIf isDarwin { home.file.".config/app".source = "${homeDir}/Library/..."; })
];
```

### Derivation

```nix
{ lib, stdenv, fetchurl, openssl }:
stdenv.mkDerivation {
  pname = "mypkg"; version = "1.0";
  src = fetchurl { url = "..."; sha256 = lib.fakeSha256; };
  buildInputs = [ openssl ];
  meta = { description = "Demo"; license = lib.licenses.mit; };
}
```

---

## 🚫 Avoid These!

### Never use rec:

```nix
# ❌ rec { a = 1; b = a + 1; }
# ✅
let a = 1; in { inherit a; b = a + 1; }
```

### Never destructure with `with`:

```nix
# ❌ args: with args; stdenv.mkDerivation { ... }
# ✅ { stdenv, fetchurl, ... }: stdenv.mkDerivation { ... }
```

