## 🔖 Common Option Types

```nix
lib.types.bool | lib.types.str | lib.types.int
lib.types.package | lib.types.listOf type
lib.types.attrsOf type | lib.types.path
lib.types.nullOr type | lib.types.enum [...]
lib.types.submodule { ... }
```

---

> Verbosity is a **feature**: code is machine-parseable and always self-documenting.

